## <a id='overview'></a> Overview

AppDynamics Platform Monitoring for Pivotal Cloud Foundry (PCF) provides visibility into the PCF platform where your AppDynamics-monitored applications are deployed. The tile allows you to deploy a Firehose Nozzle Agent that collects various KPI metrics and
a Dashboard that automatically creates health-rules and custom dashboards associated with the metrics.


